20:53.269 --> 20:55.777
They'll be ready for you
in 20 minutes, Mr. Garland.

20:57.025 --> 20:57.995
Great.

20:58.115 --> 20:59.938
I'm a star!

20:59.972 --> 21:01.373
Give me that.

21:01.407 --> 21:04.242
I will not be mitigated.

21:09.254 --> 21:10.348
Okay, you know what?

21:10.383 --> 21:12.100
I'm not coming out of
this trailer

21:12.135 --> 21:14.419
until I get a new trailer.

21:17.133 --> 21:19.149
And get me
a granola bar!

